text: A wallaroo is a medium-sized marsupial found in Australia. It can also be: * Wallaroo, New South Wales a rural locality near Canberra in New South Wales in Australia * Wallaroo, South Australia (disambiguation), articles associated with the town and locality * Wallaroo, Western Australia a town in Australia * The "Wallaroos", the Australia women's national rugby union team * HMS Wallaroo (1890), a Pearl class cruiser active off Australia before World War I * HMAS Wallaroo, a Bathurst class corvette sunk in a collision during World War II * Wallaroo, a Sydney K-class ferry
title: Wallaroo (disambiguation)
